    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 2 Minutes. One Shot at Glory.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Super Star Shooter Classic</strong> is a <strong>score-attack vertical shooter</strong> designed for pure, fast-paced arcade action.<br>Play for <strong>2 or 5 minutes</strong>, dodge intricate bullet patterns, and chase perfection in every run.<br>Short, intense, and endlessly replayable — a true retro challenge reborn.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2-Minute / 5-Minute Modes</strong> – Perfect for short, focused play sessions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online Leaderboards</strong> – Compete with players worldwide.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beautiful Pixel Art</strong> – Hand-crafted visuals inspired by the X68000 era.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Boss Battles</strong> – Learn, dodge, and strike back.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple Controls, Deep Scoring</strong> – Easy to pick up, hard to master.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Deck Ready</strong> – Quick sessions, full arcade intensity.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Recommended For</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players who enjoy <strong>score-chasing</strong> and time-attack challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fans of <strong>retro pixel shooters</strong> and <strong>arcade-style gameplay</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Those who want a short yet serious gameplay experience anywhere.</p></li></ul>",
